            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>Imp</abbr><ex>eratori</ex></expan> Caesari divi Hadriani filio divi Traiani Parthici nepoti</supplied> divi Nervae pronepoti Tito Aelio Hadriano Antonino A<supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>ug</abbr><ex>usto</ex></expan> Pi</supplied>o pontifici <expan><abbr>ma<supplied reason="lost">x</supplied>im</abbr><ex>o</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>trib</abbr><ex>unicia</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>pot</abbr><ex>estate</ex></expan> XVIII co<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>uli</ex></expan> II<supplied reason="lost">I</supplied>I <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>atri</ex></expan><certainty match="preceding-sibling::node()" locus="value"/> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>atriae</ex></expan><certainty match="preceding-sibling::node()" locus="value"/> e<supplied reason="lost" cert="low">t</supplied> <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arco</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/><supplied reason="lost">Aurelio Vero Caesari <expan><abbr>co</abbr><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>uli</ex></expan></supplied> II civitas Histrianorum <expan><abbr>T</abbr><ex>ito</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Fl</abbr><ex>avio</ex></expan> Longino <expan><abbr>Q</abbr><ex>uinto</ex></expan> Marcio Tur<supplied reason="lost">bone legato <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>usti</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>pr</abbr><ex>o</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>pr</abbr><ex>aetore</ex></expan></supplied> </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> <supplied reason="lost">Αὐτοκράτορι Καίσαρι θεοῦ Ἁδριανοῦ υἱῷ θεοῦ Τραιανοῦ Παρθι</supplied>κοῦ υἱ&amp;lt;ω&amp;gt;νῷ θεοῦ &amp;lt;Νέρουα ἐ&amp;gt;γγόνῳ Τ(ίτον) Αἴλιον Ἁδριανὸν <lb n="2"/>Ἀντωνείνῳ Σεβ(αστῷ) Εὐ<supplied reason="lost">σ</supplied>εβ(εῖ) π<supplied reason="lost">ατρὶ πατ</supplied>ρίδος ἀρχειερεῖ μεγίστῳ δημαρχικῆς ἐξουσ<supplied reason="lost">ία</supplied>ς <supplied reason="lost">τ</supplied>ὸ ιηʹ <lb n="3"/><supplied reason="lost">ὑπάτῳ τὸ δʹ καὶ Μ(άρκῳ) Αὐρηλίῳ Οὐήρῳ Κ</supplied>αίσαρι ὑπάτῳ τὸ ∙ βʹ ∙ βουλὴ δῆμος Ἰστριανῶν Τ(ίτου) ∙ Φλα(ουίου) Λογ<supplied reason="lost">γίνο</supplied>υ ∙ <lb n="4"/>Μαρ<supplied reason="lost">κ</supplied>ίῳ Τούρβωνος πρεσβευτ<supplied reason="lost">οῦ</supplied> Σε<supplied reason="lost">βαστοῦ</supplied> καὶ ἀντιστρατήγου
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Die Inschrift wurde auf drei separate Steine angebracht, wovon nur zwei noch heute vorhanden sind.</p>
